    <Paragraph FontSize="22">Prerequisites
    </Paragraph>

    <Paragraph>To run the examples in this topic, you should understand how to write WPF applications. For more information, see <Hyperlink NavigateUri="b96bed40-8946-4285-8fe4-88045ab854ed.xaml">Get Started Using Windows Presentation Foundation</Hyperlink>
. You should also understand how styles are used in WPF. For more information, see <Hyperlink NavigateUri="481765e5-5467-4a75-9f7b-e10e2ac410d9.xaml">Styling and Templating</Hyperlink>
.
    </Paragraph>

    <Paragraph FontSize="22">Expander ControlTemplate Example
    </Paragraph>

    <Paragraph>While this example contains all of the elements that are defined in the <Run FontWeight="Bold">ControlTemplate</Run>
 of an <Run FontWeight="Bold">Expander</Run>
 by default, the specific values should be thought of as examples.
    </Paragraph>

    <Table CellSpacing="5">
      <TableRowGroup>
        <TableRow>
          <TableCell>
            <Paragraph FontSize="22"><Run>XAML </Run>

            </Paragraph>

          </TableCell>

        </TableRow>

        <TableRow>
          <TableCell>
            <Paragraph xml:space="preserve" TextAlignment="Left" FontSize="8pt" FontFamily="Courier New"><Run>
&lt;ControlTemplate x:Key="ExpanderToggleButton" TargetType="{x:Type ToggleButton}"> 
&lt;Border Name="Border" CornerRadius="2,0,0,0" Background="Transparent" BorderBrush="{StaticResource NormalBorderBrush}" BorderThickness="0,0,1,0"> 
&lt;Path Name="Arrow" Fill="{StaticResource GlyphBrush}" HorizontalAlignment="Center" VerticalAlignment="Center" Data="M 0 0 L 4 4 L 8 0 Z"/> 
&lt;/Border> 
&lt;ControlTemplate.Triggers> 
&lt;Trigger Property="ToggleButton.IsMouseOver" Value="true"> 
&lt;Setter TargetName="Border" Property="Background" Value="{StaticResource DarkBrush}" /> 
&lt;/Trigger> 
&lt;Trigger Property="IsPressed" Value="true"> 
&lt;Setter TargetName="Border" Property="Background" Value="{StaticResource PressedBrush}" /> 
&lt;/Trigger> 
&lt;Trigger Property="IsChecked" Value="true"> 
&lt;Setter TargetName="Arrow" Property="Data" Value="M 0 4 L 4 0 L 8 4 Z" /> 
&lt;/Trigger> 
&lt;Trigger Property="IsEnabled" Value="False"> 
&lt;Setter TargetName="Border" Property="Background" Value="{StaticResource DisabledBackgroundBrush}" /> 
&lt;Setter TargetName="Border" Property="BorderBrush" Value="{StaticResource DisabledBorderBrush}" /> 
&lt;Setter Property="Foreground" Value="{StaticResource DisabledForegroundBrush}"/> 
&lt;Setter TargetName="Arrow" Property="Fill" Value="{StaticResource DisabledForegroundBrush}" /> 
&lt;/Trigger> 
&lt;/ControlTemplate.Triggers> 
&lt;/ControlTemplate> 
&lt;Style TargetType="{x:Type Expander}"> 
&lt;Setter Property="Template"> 
&lt;Setter.Value> 
&lt;ControlTemplate TargetType="{x:Type Expander}"> 
&lt;Grid> 
&lt;Grid.RowDefinitions> 
&lt;RowDefinition Height="Auto"/> 
&lt;RowDefinition Name="ContentRow" Height="0"/> 
&lt;/Grid.RowDefinitions> 
&lt;Border Name="Border" Grid.Row="0" Background="{StaticResource LightBrush}" BorderBrush="{StaticResource NormalBorderBrush}" BorderThickness="1" CornerRadius="2,2,0,0" > 
&lt;Grid> 
&lt;Grid.ColumnDefinitions> 
&lt;ColumnDefinition Width="20" /> 
&lt;ColumnDefinition Width="*" /> 
&lt;/Grid.ColumnDefinitions> 
&lt;ToggleButton IsChecked="{Binding Path=IsExpanded,Mode=TwoWay,RelativeSource={RelativeSource TemplatedParent}}" OverridesDefaultStyle="True" Template="{StaticResource ExpanderToggleButton}" Background="{StaticResource NormalBrush}" /> 
&lt;ContentPresenter Grid.Column="1" Margin="4" ContentSource="Header" RecognizesAccessKey="True" /> 
&lt;/Grid> 
&lt;/Border> 
&lt;Border Name="Content" Grid.Row="1" Background="{StaticResource WindowBackgroundBrush}" BorderBrush="{StaticResource SolidBorderBrush}" BorderThickness="1,0,1,1" CornerRadius="0,0,2,2" > 
&lt;ContentPresenter Margin="4" /> 
&lt;/Border> 
&lt;/Grid> 
&lt;ControlTemplate.Triggers> 
&lt;Trigger Property="IsExpanded" Value="True"> 
&lt;Setter TargetName="ContentRow" Property="Height" Value="{Binding ElementName=Content,Path=DesiredHeight}" /> 
&lt;/Trigger> 
&lt;Trigger Property="IsEnabled" Value="False"> 
&lt;Setter TargetName="Border" Property="Background" Value="{StaticResource DisabledBackgroundBrush}" /> 
&lt;Setter TargetName="Border" Property="BorderBrush" Value="{StaticResource DisabledBorderBrush}" /> 
&lt;Setter Property="Foreground" Value="{StaticResource DisabledForegroundBrush}"/> 
&lt;/Trigger> 
&lt;/ControlTemplate.Triggers> 
&lt;/ControlTemplate> 
&lt;/Setter.Value> 
&lt;/Setter> 
&lt;/Style> </Run>

            </Paragraph>

          </TableCell>

        </TableRow>

      </TableRowGroup>

    </Table>

    <Paragraph>The above example uses one or more of the following resources:
    </Paragraph>

